{"tid":169322,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"「一日冚包散」同「含笑半步釘」兩者毒性邊個勁啲?","createTime":"2017-03-24T06:30:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-24T12:07:23.000Z","uid":69133,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0737f12290c1bcebc63dd462bb64265dec58122a","tid":169322,"uid":69133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T06:30:04.000Z","msg":"有無人解答到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b331c16435dc7708aa4690c705464716bf9af242","tid":169322,"uid":16783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T07:10:10.000Z","msg":"一日冚包散係用七種唔同慨毒蟲，再加埋鶴頂紅，提煉七七四十九日而成，無色無味，殺人於無影無踪。<br />\n而含笑半步釘係用蜂蜜，川貝，桔梗，加上天山雪蓮配製而成，無須冷藏，亦不含防腐劑，除咗毒性猛烈之外，味道重好好添。"},{"pid":"545f23a492a030b3de6f4210ab70d9254852f27e","tid":169322,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T07:17:54.000Z","msg":"我愛一碌葛最勁"},{"pid":"0d32dbf23f2b99e1dbc6ea1c19641869caf703cc","tid":169322,"uid":35831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T07:30:55.000Z","msg":"如果含笑半步釘唔係假嘅話，一定係含笑半步釘毒啲，食完再引佢笑就已經搞掂"},{"pid":"4b76c1f0e460139dff49db0ad250f4cc76fb97c2","tid":169322,"uid":69133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T11:58:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我愛一碌葛最勁</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"592fb92ef52091c149de77e07a0c5a66e22febf3","tid":169322,"uid":14275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T12:02:22.000Z","msg":"淫賤不能移"},{"pid":"009cda43c6a9c0937cef2c6278633d23e4bb35c8","tid":169322,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T12:07:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我愛一碌葛最勁</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/24/200715_cef6d7c95161cda6ef78aa45535a40bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=h